<section class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20 px-6 bg-navy flex items-center">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <div>
        <span class="inline-block font-mono text-xs text-teal uppercase tracking-widest border border-teal/40 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
          EU AI Act · Enforcement: August 2026
        </span>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          The EU AI Act is enforced in August.<br />
          <span class="text-slate-light">Most Irish SMEs don't even have an AI inventory.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-slate-light text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg">
          Fixed-fee AI Act readiness for small businesses and charities across Europe. From inventory to classification to EU-hosted deployment — without the Big Four invoice.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start sm:items-center mb-10">
